{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "Template Validation Hook",
  "description": "Validates Django template syntax and PicoCSS compliance when HTML templates are saved",
  "version": "1",
  "when": {
    "type": "fileEdited",
    "patterns": [
      "templates/**/*.html",
      "verifast_app/templates/**/*.html"
    ]
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Django template modified. Please validate:\n\n1. **Template Syntax**: Check for unclosed tags, proper variable syntax, template inheritance\n2. **PicoCSS Compliance**: Ensure semantic HTML structure and proper CSS class usage\n3. **VeriFast Integration**: Verify context variable usage, XP system integration\n4. **Forms**: Check for missing CSRF tokens and proper form structure\n5. **Accessibility**: Validate HTML structure for accessibility compliance\n\nReport specific issues found and suggest corrections."
  }
}